Package ru.nsu.fit.smolyakov.snakegame.properties

Record Class GameProperties

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
ru.nsu.fit.smolyakov.snakegame.properties.GameProperties
Record Components:
width - a width of the game field
height - a height of the game field
javaFxScaling - a resolution scaling of JavaFX. This value determines, how many pixels every cell will take both in width and height. For example, if the value is 8, then every cell will take 8x8 pixels
apples - a number of apples
level - one of possible Level subclasses
aiClassNamesList - a list of AI class names, each of them located in GameData.AI_SNAKES_PACKAGE_NAME package
speed - a game speed
public record GameProperties(int width, int height, int javaFxScaling, int apples, Level level, List<String> aiClassNamesList, GameSpeed speed) extends Record
Represents properties of presenter.
